Package: libbno055-linux-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libbno055-linux1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libbno055-linux
 A robust, thread-safe, and dependency-free C++17 library for the
 BNO055 sensor over I2C on Linux. This package contains the headers
 and CMake configuration files required for development.

Package: libbno055-linux1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Shared library for libbno055-linux
 A robust, thread-safe, and dependency-free C++17 library for the
 BNO055 sensor over I2C on Linux. This package contains the compiled
 shared library.
